---
layout: default
title: Disruption 2020 // Curtin Grad Show
pagination:
    data: studentData
    size: 1
    alias: student
permalink: "student/{{ student.id }}/"
description: Disruption 2020 features graduates across the majors of Animation & Game Design, Creative Advertising & Graphic Design, Digital Design, and Illustration. Our time at Curtin University has not been without disruption, having spent the bulk of first semester fully online during the pandemic lockdown. The return to campus was a momentous occasion for us final year students. It only served to shift our beautifully warped minds into even more creative territory. Friendships were formed, nicknames were earned, and skills were refined. 
---

<div data-title="{% if student.name.preferred %}{{ student.name.preferred }}{% else %}{{ student.name.first }}{% endif %} {{ student.name.last }} // Disruption 2020 // Curtin Grad Show">
    <div class="student-columns dark min-h-900 mb-0 mt-0">
        <div class="profile-col-left page-padding-left is-flex flex-column">
            <div class="layout-main z-1 fadein mb-6">
                <h4 class="is-size-5 is-size-6-mobile mb-3 max-w-600 transition-fadeout">{{ student.majors | join(", ", "title") }}</h4>
                <h1 class="title is-size-1 is-size-4-mobile is-uppercase mb-2">
                    {% if student.name.preferred %}{{ student.name.preferred }}{% else %}{{ student.name.first }}{% endif %} {{ student.name.last }}
                </h1>
                <p class="max-w-600 transition-fadeout">{{ student.statement }}</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-2 is-relative z-1">
                <p class="max-w-600 mb-2 transition-fadeout">
                    {{ student.bio }}
                </p>
                
                <div class="port-info w-full mt-6 max-w-600">
                    {% if student.portfolio %}
                        <a href="{{ student.portfolio }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                            <button class="button is-white is-medium">Portfolio</button>
                        </a>
                    {% endif %}
                    <div class="social-icons items-center layout-main">
                        {% for social in student.social %}
                            <a href="{{ social.link }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                            {% if socialIcons[social.name] %}    
                                <i class="fab {{ socialIcons[social.name] }}"></i>
                            {% else %}
                                <span>{{ social.name.substring(0, 2) }}<span>
                            {% endif %}
                            </a>        
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="major-orbs entry-slidein">
            {% for major in student.majors %}
                {% if majorImages[major.id] %}
                    <img src="{{ majorImages[major.id] }}">                    
                {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="px-0 py-0 portfolio-image profile-headshot headshot-hover">
            {% if student.headshots.fun %}
                <img src="{{ student.headshots.fun }}" class="student-headshot wide-min-h-full stacked-max-h-600" alt="{{ student.name.first }} {{ student.name.last }} Headshot">            
                <img src="{{ student.headshots.pro }}" class="student-headshot headshot-pro wide-min-h-full stacked-max-h-600" alt="{{ student.name.first }} {{ student.name.last }} Headshot">
            {% else %}
                <img src="{{ student.headshots.pro }}" class="student-headshot wide-min-h-full stacked-max-h-600" alt="{{ student.name.first }} {{ student.name.last }} Headshot">
            {% endif %}
        </div>
    </div>
    {% if projects %} 
        <div class="student-image-grid page-padding-all has-background-white">
            {% for project in projects %}
                <img src="{{ project.src }}" alt="{{ project.alt }}">
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    {% endif %}
</div>